airmon-ng start wlan0 ==========> monitor mode will start

airmon-ng check kill ============>2nd step


===========FOR DELETING WLN0 AFTER MONITOR MODE=============
iw dev wlan0 interface del

=============FOR ENABLE WLAN0 AFTER DELETING============
iw phy phy0 interface add wlan0 type managed

============= service NetworkManager start =============
service NetworkManager start 
